Type: Package
Package: confidenceCurves
Title: Frequentist Confidence Analysis for Clinical Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Freda",
                    family = "Werdiger",
                    role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "freda.werdiger@unimelb.edu.au")
Maintainer: Freda Werdiger <freda.werdiger@unimelb.edu.au>
Description: Frequentist confidence analysis answers the question: How
    confident in a particular treatment effect?  This package calculate
    the frequentist confidence in a specified treatment effect for a point
    estimate and error estimate that is either directly provided, or
    calculated.  In addition to returning the level of confidence in
    specified effects, makeConfidenceCurves also returns the family of
    confidence curves associated with the observed effect.
